    <!-- Onboarding / registration -->
    <string name="privacy_title">Your Privacy Matters</string>
    <string name="privacy_body">
        Kabu-Kabu is a privacy-first P2P taxi and courier service.\n\n
        • Your exact GPS location is NEVER stored or transmitted.\n
          We only use a ~5 km fuzzy zone (GeoHash cell) for matching.\n\n
        • Your phone number is hashed (SHA-256) on this device.\n
          The plaintext number is never sent over any network.\n\n
        • All peer traffic is routed through the I2P anonymity network.\n
          No driver or courier can see your IP address.\n\n
        • All trip records are stored on your device only.\n
          No cloud database. No central server. No data broker.\n\n
        By accepting you agree to these privacy principles.
    </string>
